      </div>
      <h3>Fetch</h3>
      <p>DeFiLlama API — every 5 minutes</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipeline-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="pipeline-step">
      <div class="step-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 3H2l8 9.46V19l4 2v-8.54L22 3z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Filter</h3>
      <p>Quality gates — TVL, outliers, APY</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipeline-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="pipeline-step">
      <div class="step-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Cache</h3>
      <p>SQLite with WAL mode</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipeline-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="pipeline-step">
      <div class="step-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6m8 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0h6m0 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Score</h3>
      <p>10-factor risk model (0–100)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pipeline-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="pipeline-step">
      <div class="step-icon">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9"/></svg>
      </div>
